ew_type=Standard&amp;template=Roundups&amp;module=content-body&amp;element=offer&amp;item=text-link&amp;element_label=angled&amp;short_url=a5bXwV&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Flifehacker.com%2Ffeed%2Frss" rel="nofollow sponsored" target="_blank" title="在新窗口中打开">有角度</a>或<a href="https://zdcs.link/QODgbE?pageview_type=Standard&amp;template=Roundups&amp;module=content-body&amp;element=offer&amp;item=text-link&amp;element_label=flat&amp;short_url=QODgbE&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Flifehacker.com%2Ffeed%2Frss" rel="nofollow sponsored" target="_blank" title="在新窗口中打开">平坦</a>的，具体取决于您的喜好以及您需要扫过的障碍物的数量。这些的好处是它们非常紧凑，也易于存放，而且没有刷毛，不会在衣柜里弯曲变形。</p><h2 id="other-broom-options-and-notes">其他扫帚选项和注意事项</h2><p>我倾向于那种多层的、毛茸茸的扫帚，但是当我在它和硅胶扫帚之间犹豫不决时，我将分享我在研究中发现的其他一些可能很适合您的需求的扫帚。 </p><div class="shadow-b-2 mb-4 rounded-md border-2 border-[#F0F0F0] px-6 py-2 shadow-lg md:px-12" role="region" aria-label="Products List" x-data="{ showMore: false }"><div class="flex w-full flex-col flex-nowrap justify-center gap-2 text-black no-underline md:order-2 md:gap-y-6"><div class="flex flex-col justify-between gap-y-2 md:w-full md:gap-y-1"><div class="block w-fit cursor-pointer font-akshar text-lg font-medium leading-5 text-brand-green duration-200 ease-in-out hover:text-brand-green-700 md:text-xl md:leading-6"> FURemover 原装室内宠物毛发橡胶扫帚，带地毯耙、橡胶扫帚和毛巾</div></div><div class="hidden md:flex md:justify-between md:gap-x-4"><div class="w-full mb-0 md:flex md:flex-col md:justify-center font-sans leading-4 text-black"><div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-x-1 md:justify-start"><span class="font-bold"><span class="font-medium">亚马逊</span>13.99 美元</span><img class="mt-0 h-[15px]" src="/images/amazon-prime.svg" title="亚马逊 Prime" alt="Amazon Prime"></div></div> <button class="flex justify-center items-center w-full bg-brand-green text-white text-base font-sans font-medium rounded-md hover:bg-brand-green-700 hover:cursor-pointer md:text-sm hidden self-end h-12 max-w-[10rem] duration-200 ease-in-out hover:bg-brand-gree